OL,5, For decades the huge monolithic block  
OL,6, of granite in the middle of the        
OL,7, cemetery in the Swiss town of Chur was 
OL,8, ignored by passers-by; no one seemed to
OL,9, know quite what it was.                
OL,11,FBut the 13-tonne stone monument that   
OL,12,Fdwarfs the nearby gravestones is now   
OL,13,Fcausing controversy - and              
OL,14,Fembarrassment.                         
OL,16,FResearch by a local journalist has     
OL,17,Frevealed links to Nazi Germany, and to 
OL,18,Fneutral Switzerland's own awkward      
OL,19,Frelations with its World War Two       
OL,20,Fneighbours.                            
